// WorkItemsList
// Lists work items for the current session and shows the task graph card during the implementation phase.
// The task graph can be dismissed via a close button.

FUNCTION handleCloseTaskGraph()
  Hides the task graph card by clearing its visible state.

---

FUNCTION WorkItemsList(props) -> ReactNode                                EXPORT
  CALLS: useSessionStore (sessionStore), TaskGraphCard (TaskGraphCard)
  Reads the current session and its work items from sessionStore.
  IF the session is in the implementation phase and the task graph is visible, renders TaskGraphCard above the items list.
  Renders the list of work items with status indicators.
  Provides a button to close the task graph via handleCloseTaskGraph.
